Foundation.AI.Experiment
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The Foundation.AI.Experiment module is a C# port and generalization of
"autoresearch" by Andrej Karpathy:

    https://github.com/karpathy/autoresearch

The original Python implementation is licensed under the MIT License.
The experiment-loop architecture (read code -> propose modification -> commit ->
run -> accept-if-improved / revert-if-worse -> log -> repeat) is preserved;
the .NET implementation generalizes the agent, runner, and metric-parser
behind interfaces so any LLM provider, experiment runner, and scoring metric
can be plugged in.

